2. Footfall Predictor This tool was developed as a part of the Surf Project funded by ESRC Future Research Leaders scheme. The tool, named as Leeds Footfall Predictor, built on the work led by Nick Malleson which determined that the daily footfall rates observed in the Leeds city centre can be explained in terms of external variables, such as temperature, rainfall and holidays.
